[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ Pattern #8: Greek Gift Sacrifices (Bxh7+ sacrifice!!) }
1. Bxh7+!! Kxh7 { We now swing over the queen to h4 } 2. Qh4+ Kg6 { We now play Qg5+ } 3. Qg5+ Kh7 { Play Qh5+ } 4. Qh5+ Kg8 { We now play Ng5 } 5. Ng5 Bxf2+ { Take the bishop with the king or bishop (doesn't matter) } 6. Kxf2 f6 { It is now mate on h7! GG! } { [%csl Bh7][%cal Bh5h7] } 7. Qh7# { GG! That all she wrote.
--Point--
You want to sacrifice to expose their king and then you just mate them or win a lot of material. } *


