1. d4 Nf6 { [%csl Bf4][%cal Bc1f4] } 2. Bf4 c5 { [%csl Bd5][%cal Bd4d5] } 3. d5 e6 { [%csl Bc4][%cal Bc2c4] } 4. c4 { We need to support our center. } 4... exd5 5. cxd5 d6 { [%csl Bc3][%cal Bb1c3] } 6. Nc3 g6 { [%csl Be4][%cal Be2e4] } 7. e4 Bg7 { [%csl Bf3][%cal Bg1f3] } 8. Nf3 O-O { [%csl Bd2][%cal Bf3d2] } 9. Nd2 Re8 { [%csl Be2][%cal Bf1e2] } 10. Be2 a6 { [%csl Ba4][%cal Ba2a4] } 11. a4 $16 { The pawn on d6 is weak and we are better after moves such as f3 followed by Nc4 and we will win the d6 pawn.
--Point--
